{"cid":"1572072504832002","cha_name":"王一博","desc":"王一博，中国内地男歌手、演员、职业摩托车赛车手，1997年8月5日出生于河南洛阳。2014年9月15日，作为UNIQ组合成员出道，2016年4月加入《天天向上》。第30届中国电视金鹰奖观众喜爱的男演员。《陪你到世界之巅》饰季向空，《陈情令》饰蓝忘机，《有翡》饰谢允，《冰雨火》饰陈宇，《风起洛阳》饰百里弘毅。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1572072504832002","author":{"uid":"101562100101","short_id":"2014940272","nickname":"王一博吧_WYBBar","gender":1,"signature":"王一博是最酷的盖","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866","url_list":["https://p9.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866","url_list":["https://p6.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verif {"cid":"1601854469066760","cha_name":"刘宇宁","desc":"刘宇宁，1990年1月8日出生于辽宁省丹东市，中国内地流行乐男歌手、影视演员，{摩登兄弟}乐队主唱。\r\n2014年，担任摩登兄弟的主唱。2015年，随摩登兄弟入驻YY平台。2016年，主演个人首部电影《{九五2班}》，从而正式进入演艺圈。2017年，随摩登兄弟由室内转入街头直播；同年，其主演的犯罪悬疑电影《{秦贼有道}》上映。2018年，其主演的青春励志爱情电影《{罗曼蒂克振兴史}》上映；同年，出演个人首部影视剧《{租界少年热血档案}》；9月15日，推出首支个人单曲《{想象[摩登兄弟刘宇宁第一首单曲]}》。2019年，成为湖南卫视音乐竞技节目《{歌手2019}》首位“全民举荐踢馆歌手”；3月25日，获得第26届东方风云榜音乐盛典最佳新锐歌手奖、网络影响力荣誉奖，而其演唱的歌曲《让酒》则获得传媒推荐影视歌曲奖；4月27日，获得第23届全球华语榜中榜年度最佳新人奖；同年，发布首张个人音乐专辑《十》；8月30日，获得华人歌曲音乐盛典年度最佳新人奖。2020年1月8日，获得2019今日头条“年度新势力明星”荣誉。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1601854469066760","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","uniqu
